<div class="banner">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="main-text">
      <h1>View properties instantly,<br>
      anytime, anywhere.</h1>
      <p>Connecting buyers and sellers <br>
      without any third-party worries.</p>
      <form action="/listings"><input type="text" id="location-input-homepage" name="location" required
          minlength="3" maxlength="25" placeholder="Where would you like to buy your property?">
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container mt-3">

  <h3 class="m-5 text-center" >Check out some of our current available instant viewings:</h3>
  <section class="mb-3">
    <div class="main-container d-flex">
      <div class="row">
        <%= render 'shared/card', listings:@listings %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <%= link_to "See all of our current listings..",  listings_path, class:"homepage-a" %>

  <br>
  <br>
  <br>
  <br>

  <section id="benefits">
    <h2 class="text-center">Benefits</h2>
    <br>
    <div class="d-flex">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <div class="card-benefits">
            <img src="https://www.thehouseshop.com/property-blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/house-hunt.jpg" alt="Instant Viewings">
            <div class="card-info-benefits p-1">
              <h3>Instant Viewing</h3>
              <p class="text-justify p-1">You can book property viewings really easily; all you need to do is to create a Viewprop account. Pick a property with the tag <strong>'instant viewing'</strong> and you're good to go.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <div class="card-benefits">
            <img src="https://cdn.dnaindia.com/sites/default/files/styles/full/public/2019/04/16/813736-homeloan-istock-041719.jpg" alt="Cheap Listings">
            <div class="card-info-benefits p-1">
              <h3>Cheap Listing</h3>
              <p class="text-justify p-1">You can <strong>get all the benefits</strong> of booking a real estate agent without the unnecessary expenses. With a <strong>low fixed-fee</strong>, you never have to worry about the additional costs of selling a house. </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <div class="card-benefits">
            <img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/photos/looking-for-bike-shops-nearby-picture-id1069962264?b=1&k=20&m=1069962264&s=170667a&w=0&h=Mjtnu6ZrdC9XXJvaOTsS22VLeVuTNA4Ds8Vjo8ExcJc=" alt="Person holding phone">
            <div class="card-info-benefits p-1">
              <h3>All-in-One App</h3>
              <p class="text-justify p-1">Search for listings, book a viewing, place an offer, and put your down-payment all in one app. A contract is also auto-generated to help you <strong>sell your listings right away!</strong></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <br>
  <br>
  <br>
  <br>

  <section id="how-it-works">
    <h2 class="text-center">How It Works</h2>
    <br>
    <div class="d-flex">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-3">
          <div class="card-work align-items-center p-3 m-1">
            <h2 class="text-center"><i class="fas fa-search-location"></i></h2>
            <br>
            <h3 class="text-center">Search for a Listing</h3>
            <p class="text-justify">Start your search from the location of the properties you hope to purchase from!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-3">
          <div class="card-work align-items-center p-3 m-1">
            <h2 class="text-center"><i class="far fa-calendar-alt"></i></h2>
            <br>
            <h3 class="text-center">Book a Viewing</h3>
            <p class="text-justify">Viewings will be arranged remotely and you can access the property with a security key provided!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-3">
          <div class="card-work align-items-center p-3 m-1">
            <h2 class="text-center"><i class="fas fa-comments-dollar"></i></h2>
            <br>
            <h3 class="text-center">Place an Offer</h3>
            <p class="text-justify">If you see a property you are interested in, you can instantly message and negotiate with the owner to place an offer!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-3">
          <div class="card-work align-items-center p-3 m-1">
            <h2 class="text-center"><i class="far fa-credit-card"></i></h2>
            <br>
            <h3 class="text-center">Secure Payment</h3>
            <p class="text-justify">Place a down payment on the property through our safe payment gateway system and you're all set!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <br>
  <br>
  <br>
  <br>

  <section id="about_us" class="m-3">
    <h2 class="text-center">About Us</h2>
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="text-justify">Viewprop is an online platform to browse and purchase listings instantly from anywhere in the world. Get the benefits of creating instant bookings and getting great deals without the hassle of a middle-man. Viewprop is focused on creating the best user-experience for homebuyers and property listers, so that real-estate can be accessible for everyone.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-cards">
        <div class="about-card">
          <%= image_tag 'oli.jpeg', class: "about-avatar" %>
          <h5>Olivier Roper</h5>
          <p>Founder</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-card">
          <%= image_tag 'shania.jpeg', class: "about-avatar" %>
          <h5>Shania Tsamara</h5>
          <p>Lead Developer</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-card">
          <%= image_tag 'brian.jpeg', class: "about-avatar" %>
          <h5>Brian Koekkoek</h5>
          <p>Promising Intern</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="text-justify">Three individuals who got together in the Le Wagon Coding Bootcamp and decided to work on the Viewprop project together. With different nationalities and personalities, the application encompasses all the necessary functions needed to properly purchase a property anywhere in the world.</p>
      </div>
  </section>
  <br>
  <br>
  <br>
</div>
